.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

House: wooden, tower, townhouse, farmhouse, modern
The people use 5 different means of transport: subway, scooter, quad-bike, ship, airplane
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: volleyball, soccer, sailing, ice-hockey, surfing
There 5 different types of food: woodenmaster, cabbage, blueberry, plum, watermelon
City: boston, nizza, berlin, new-york, prague
1. the person driving the subway is the townhouse house
2. the person driving the swedish is the person traveling to berlin
3. the person driving the scooter is the person who's sport is ice-hockey
4. the tower house is on the left of the farmhouse house
5. the tower house is the person who's sport is soccer
6. the person eating blueberry is the person traveling to nizza
7. the modern house is the person eating cabbage
8. the person who's sport is sailing is in the middle
9. the person driving the ship is on the far left
10. the person eating watermelon is on the left or right of the person traveling to boston
11. the person traveling to pragues is on the left or right of the person eating cabbage
12. the person eating woodenmaster is the person who's sport is volleyball
13. the person driving the quad-bike is the person eating plum
14. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the wooden house
15. the person eating watermelon is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing

.:: Answer ::.
